<h1><code ng:non-bindable="">jqmPopup</code>
<div><span class="hint">directive in module <code ng:non-bindable="">jqm</code>
</span>
</div>
</h1>
<div><h2 id="description">Description</h2>
<div class="description"><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpopup-page"><p>Creates a popup with the given content.  The popup can be opened and closed on an element using <a href="#/api/jqm.directive:jqmPopupTarget">jqmPopupTarget</a>.</p>
<p>Tip: put a <a href="#/api/jqm.directive:jqmView">jqmView</a> inside a popup to have full scrollable pages inside.
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
&lt;div jqm-popup="myPopup"&gt;
  &lt;div jqm-view="{
  templateUrl: 'views/my-popup-content-page.html',
  controller: 'MyPopupController'
  }"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
</div></div>
<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>
<div class="usage">as attribute<pre class="prettyprint linenums">&lt;ANY jqm-popup="{expression}"
     [animation="{expression}"]
     [placement="{expression}"]
     [overlay-theme="{expression}"]
     [corners="{expression}"]
     [shadow="{expression}"]&gt;
   ...
&lt;/ANY&gt;</pre>
<h4 id="usage_parameters">Parameters</h4><table class="variables-matrix table table-bordered table-striped"><thead><tr><th>Param</th><th>Type</th><th>Details</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>jqmPopup</td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-expression">expression</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpopup-page"><p>Assignable angular expression to bind this popup to.  jqmPopupTargets will point to this model.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>animation <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-expression">expression</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpopup-page"><p>jQuery Mobile animation to use to show/hide this popup.  Default &#39;fade&#39;.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>placement <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-expression">expression</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpopup-page"><p>Where to put the popup relative to its target.  Available: &#39;left&#39;, &#39;right&#39;, &#39;top&#39;, &#39;bottom&#39;, &#39;inside&#39;. Default: &#39;inside&#39;.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>overlay-theme <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-expression">expression</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpopup-page"><p>The theme to use for the overlay behind the popup. Defaults to the popup&#39;s theme.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>corners <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-expression">expression</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpopup-page"><p>Whether the popup has corners. Default true.</p>
</div></td></tr><tr><td>shadow <div><em>(optional)</em></div></td><td><a href="" class="label type-hint type-hint-expression">expression</a></td><td><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpopup-page"><p>Whether the popup has shadows. Default true.</p>
</div></td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<h2 id="example">Example</h2>
<div class="example"><div class="jqm-directive-page jqm-directive-jqmpopup-page"><h4 id="example_source">Source</h4>
<div source-edit="jqm" source-edit-deps="angular.js" source-edit-html="index.html-9" source-edit-css="" source-edit-js="" source-edit-json="" source-edit-unit="" source-edit-scenario=""></div>
<div class="tabbable"><div class="tab-pane" title="index.html">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums" ng-set-text="index.html-9" ng-html-wrap-loaded="jqm angular.js"></pre>
<script type="text/ng-template" id="index.html-9">
  <div jqm-popup="myPopup">
  Hey guys, here's a popup!
  </div>
  <div style="padding: 50px;"
   jqm-popup-target="myPopup"
   jqm-popup-model="pageCenterPop">

   <div jqm-button ng-click="pageCenterPop = true">
    Open Page Center Popup
   </div>
   <div jqm-button
     jqm-popup-target="myPopup"
     jqm-popup-model="buttonPop"
     jqm-popup-placement="left"
     ng-click="buttonPop = true">
     Open popup left of this button!
   </div>
  </div>
</script>
</div>
